Lekcia 9: 
vytvorenie tabulky pomocou /bin suboru

presunut sa do cakeproject/bin zlozky v konzoli,
com : cake migrations create table_name
vytvori migrations subor v /config/migrations/2019...._users.php

v tomto subore vytvorime tabulku :

$table = $this->table('table_name')

$table
	->addColumn('col_name','datetype',[
		'default' => 'defaultna_hodnota',
		'limit' => rozsah(int)
		'null'	=> boolean (povolenie null hodnoty v stlpci)		
	])
	->create();

datetypy - string,boolean,timestamp,datetime,integer,email...

phinx obsahuje tieto funkcie:
	->createTable
	->renameTable
	->addColumn
	->renameColumn
	->addIndex
	->addForeignKey
a metody
	public function up(){} // migrate up
	public function down(){} // migrate down

spustime :
	cake migrations migrate
vytvori tabulku..
